Class GrouperGroupInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.internet2.middleware.grouper.pspng.GrouperGroupInfo

  • public class GrouperGroupInfo
extends Object
    This is a simple class to hold name and attribute information of a group. This is useful because it provides common data whether the group is an existing group or has been deleted and the information is coming from a PITGroup
